h poached stone fruit."}],"hintsAndTricks":["If you prefer, you can replace the cream with Greek yoghurt.","These jellies can also be turned out as delicious panna cottas. Simple strain the mixture into 6 greased dariole moulds or ramekins (120 ml capacity), then place into the refrigerator until completely set. Use a knife to loosen from the mould or simply invert onto a plate with a little shake. Lower, flatter shaped moulds will generally be easier to turn out."],"basicInfo":["easy","50m","5h","6 portions"]}